These are discussed in more detail below. Once I get a steer on these I sho=
uld be able to make a good structure for the site. To get to a final polish=
ed product it would also be great to have some recordings (even if very sho=
rt), and some more pics. I have the ones from the concert in Worcester - bu=
t maybe some more informal ones from a rehearsal would complement these bes=
t.
Please do share any thoughts and i=E2=80=99ll push things on.
Best,
Will

